data.description: Great unit located in the most desirable area of Coral Springs, 3/2.5 Beautiful Townhouse in the heart of Coral Spring for all ages. Immaculate kitchen updated, with quartz counters top, stainless steel appliances, and new floors. A lot of light throughout the house, with a nice backyard. Built in 1997, close to major roads, worship places, Great school zone, shopping centers, airports, hospitals, and universities. The condominium association takes care of the roof, exterior building, and common areas. Won’t last, hurry up to call it HOME.
